name: Mardi Gras Cake
description:
A joyous Mardi Gras’ King Cake in the style of funfetti bundt cake. Of course, glazed with icing sugar and sprinkled with 3 iconic colored sugar. Not yet, we decorate with masquerades cookies, macarons, the colorful string of candy beads, and a little baby sneaking behind the whole cake.
Already mouth-watering? Let’s collect it one, two, or as many as you like.
